본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap (companion-diagnostic platform). hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 액체생검 (cell-free DNA + circulating tumor DNA + CTC + extracellular vesicle + cell-free RNA) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 진단/모니터링 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_pharmacogenomics` (variant population) + `.roadmap.disease_theranostic` (radiopharmaceutical) + `.roadmap.disease_cancer` (treatment): liquid biopsy = 액체생검 — cell-free DNA (cfDNA) + circulating tumor DNA (ctDNA) + circulating tumor cells (CTC) + extracellular vesicles + cell-free RNA. 2010s+ paradigm + 2018 Guardant360 first FDA NGS + 2024 Signatera MRD-monitoring + 2023 Galleri multi-cancer detection. 양자-VQE 의 fit: variant calling + ctDNA fragment-length + structural variation 양자 분석 — 그러나 modality 가 진단/모니터링.)

scope:
- ctDNA (circulating tumor DNA — cell-free fragment)
- cfDNA (cell-free DNA — non-tumor source)
- CTC (circulating tumor cells)
- extracellular vesicle (exosome + microvesicle)
- cell-free RNA (cfRNA + microRNA)
- minimal residual disease monitoring (MRD)
- early detection multi-cancer (MCED)
- companion diagnostic for targeted therapy
- 약물 반응 monitoring + 내성 emergence detection
- 임신 + 유전 진단 (NIPT — Down syndrome 등 cross-pediatric_rare)
- 신생아 metabolic 검사 (cross-newborn_perinatal)
- transplant monitoring (organ rejection cfDNA — donor-specific cross-transplant)
- 감염 진단 (cell-free pathogen DNA — sepsis cross-critical_care)
- 신경학 marker (NfL plasma — cross-neurodegen + dementia_specific)
- 양자-VQE 적용 (variant calling + ctDNA fragment-length 분석 양자)

