## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Guardant360 CDx 2018** = first FDA-approved NGS liquid biopsy panel. ctDNA NGS 70-300 gene 동시 분석 + tissue biopsy 대체 가능 — pan-cancer CDx 표준. quantum-VQE 의 variant calling + ultra-low VAF detection 직접 fit.
2. **FoundationOne Liquid CDx 2020** = Roche/Foundation 300+ gene ctDNA NGS — Guardant 후속 + tumor mutation burden (TMB) + microsatellite instability (MSI) 동시. CDx 영역 second-line.
3. **Signatera 2024 FDA MRD** = Natera tumor-informed MRD — 환자별 16-personalized panel ctDNA 0.01% VAF detection + adjuvant chemo decision. CRC + breast + lung 적응증. quantum-VQE 의 ultra-low VAF 검출 한계 향상이 직접 임상 의미.
4. **Galleri 2021 LDT** = GRAIL (Illumina) first MCED — methylation-based >50 cancer types 단일 채혈 + tissue-of-origin prediction. PATHFINDER + NHS-Galleri RCT 결과 2026 진행. LDT 2024 final rule 영향 cross-orphan_drug_policy.
5. **DELFI Diagnostic 2022** = fragmentomics — fragment size distribution + GC bias + repeat 분포 ML classifier. ctDNA quantification 없이 패턴-기반 MCED 가능.
6. **CellSearch 2004 first FDA CTC** = Veridex (Janssen → Menarini) EpCAM+ CTC enumeration — breast + colon + prostate metastatic prognostic. 20+ years FDA 첫 CTC. enumeration 한정 + downstream 분자분석 어려움.
7. **Parsortix 2022 FDA** = ANGLE size-based CTC capture — non-EpCAM cancer (sarcoma + EpCAM-low) viable CTC 보존 + downstream RNA-seq 가능.
8. **clonoSEQ 2018 FDA** = Adaptive Biotechnologies IgH/TCR rearrangement MRD — ALL + MM + CLL heme malig 표준. tumor-informed + 10^-6 LOD. quantum-VQE 의 immune repertoire clonal tracking.
9. **AlloSure 2017** = CareDx donor-specific cfDNA kidney transplant rejection — donor SNP discrimination cfDNA 비율 측정. heart/lung 확장. cross-transplant.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, 액체생검 modality 가 진단/모니터링 — therapeutic 약물 변환 한정.

